re eller sl\u00f8yfe navn p\u00e5 annen m\u00e5te enn etter loven her.\u00bb"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "forbruker"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "8cf446fb92c7a1476c1013146f242a96f467460418cd3788939dfc353d6c293c"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-08-02T21:15:59.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Hvem bestemmer n\u00e5r foreldrene somler?"}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article2140704.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/shutterstock_66511687_2"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/acbcb980a69eda9acf258af844e71d83b21605f6.jpg?597104f2"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["12 midtnorske barn har ikke fornavn -adressa.no", "Plikt til \u00e5 velge navn for barn", "F\u00e5r mors navn"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "acbcb980a69eda9acf258af844e71d83b21605f6"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim", "ukeadressa", "eadressa", "skattelister", "d\u00f8dsfall", "tr\u00f8nder", "trafikk"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "nyheter,trondheim,ukeadressa,eadressa,skattelister,d\u00f8dsfall,tr\u00f8nder,trafikk"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "forbruker"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "family-and-parenting"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["navn", "fornavn", "barn", "midtnorske barn"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["universitetet", "brille", "skatt s\u00f8r"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["norge", "bergen"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["inger edvardsen", "ivar utne"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "forbruker"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article2140704.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/shutterstock_66511687_2"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field